<HEADLINE> New, supposedly improved Lobbying Commission underfunded, groups  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
    	   ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) - Nine people. More than 2,000 agencies. Government
watchdog groups said that, despite the recent political rhetoric, there will be
no increased scrutiny of lobbyists in Albany until the state Lobbying Commission
gets the resources it needs.
<P>
	   The Common Cause and the League of Women Voters want Gov. George Pataki to
