markets in the United States are closed today in observance of
Martin Luther King Jr. Day. On Friday, the Dow Jones industrial
average rose 140.55 to a new closing record of 11,722.98. The
Nasdaq Composite Index rose 107.06 to 4,064.27.
</P>
